---

<Layout>
    <HeadersBanner HeadersBanners={HeaderBannerData} />
    <UmmahCharity />
    <div class="mt-12">
        <p class="text-maroon md:text-3xl font-bold text-center text-6xl">
            Help Create Livelihood Opportunities
        </p>
        <p class="text-grey text-lg font-semibold md:text-xl text-center mt-5">
            The economic statistics in Pakistan sound alarming, with approximately 24% <br>of the population living below the poverty line, a figure aggravated by the<br> impact of the economic crisis and inflation. Compounded by insufficient<br> infrastructure and limited employment prospects, the daily struggles <br>of people in remote regions present a disheartening image. <br><br>However, at Al-Wahab Foundation, we are committed to creating solutions <br>that bring hope and stability to struggling families, liberating them from<br> the poverty cycle. By offering means for a stable livelihood, we are touching <br>the lives of countless people across Pakistan. Together, we can work<br> towards a brighter and more prosperous future for those in need.
        </p>
     
    </div>

    <!--card -->
    <CardforCountry CountryCardDetails={card} />

    <!--support banner -->
    <SupportBanner BannerDetails={SupportBannerDetails} />
    <!--section n -->
    <div
        class="counter flex justify-center items-center flex-nowrap gap-6 pt-20 overflow-auto"
    >
        <!-- Item 1 -->
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center" data-aos="fade-up">
            <div>
                <img
                    src="https://via.placeholder.com/50"
                    alt="icon"
                    class="mx-auto"
                />
            </div>
            <div>
