                    src="https://via.placeholder.com/50"
                    alt="icon"
                    class="mx-auto"
                />
            </div>
            <div>
                <p
                    class="text-2xl font-bold font-hind text-blackColor dark:text-blackColor-dark"
                >
                    <span data-countup-number="1380 ">1380 </span><span
                        >+</span
                    >
                </p>
                <p
                    class="uppercase text-blackColor font-medium dark:text-blackColor-dark"
                >
                Families given a stable income
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Item 4 -->
        

        <!-- Repeat similar structure for Items 3 to 7 -->
    </div>

    <!--section 2 -->

    <!--section video -->
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 mt-16">
        <div class="relative overflow-hidden pb-[40%]">
            <iframe
                class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full"
                src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/rKE-aUoKWhE?si=Hix0Wt-am77ezPpB"
                title="YouTube video player"
                frameborder="0"
                allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share"
                referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin"
                allowfullscreen
            >
            </iframe>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- -->
    

   
    <!--section 3 -->
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="row">
            <p
                class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl text-maroon font-bold mt-10 sm:mt-20"
            >
            Why Donate to AWF’s Rozgar Project?
            </p>
            <p
                class="mt-5 sm:mt-7 text-grey text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold text-justify"
            >
            Breaking the poverty cycle in deprived communities requires innovative and sustainable change. Every individual should have the opportunity to work and earn a stable income, living with dignity alongside their families and within their communities. <br><br>However, in many parts of Pakistan, this right is difficult to attain. Rural areas, dependent on agriculture, face significant challenges when disasters strike, while social inequalities hinder access to proper education and training.<br><br>At <a href="#" class="text-maroon hover:text-customBeige font-bold">Al-Wahab Foundation</a>, our visionary founder, Mufti Abdul Wahab, leads the way in providing support to establish empowering businesses and work opportunities that build resilience against future crises. Your donation plays a vital role in creating lasting change and independence. From offering transportation that generates income to providing skills training, essential tools, and halal business loans, your contribution fosters positive, long-term impacts. Together, we can pave the path towards a brighter future for these communities.
            </p>
            
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="row">
            <p
                class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl text-maroon font-bold mt-10 sm:mt-20"
            >
            Mufti Abdul Wahab in Pakistan: Rozgar Project Distribution Event
            </p>
            <p
                class="mt-5 sm:mt-7 text-grey text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold text-justify"
            >
            Chairman Al-Wahab Foundation, Mufti Abdul Wahab recently visited Pakistan to lead a significant distribution event for the Rozgar Project. AWF’s efforts were focused on providing rickshaws and delivery motorbikes to those in need, offering them a dignified income source through the Rozgar Project. <br><br>During this visit, <a href="#" class="text-maroon hover:text-customBeige font-bold">Mufti Abdul Wahab </a> provided 24 rickshaws and 50 motorbikes, to well-deserving individuals. The chairman’s visit underscored AWF’s dedication to transforming lives and fostering sustainable empowerment within the communities it serves.
            </p>
            
        </div>
    </div>

    <RestoringLives ReStroingLives={Restoring} />
    
    <!--section 5  -->
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="row">
            <p
                class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl text-maroon font-bold mt-10 sm:mt-20"
            >
            How is Al-Wahab Foundation Creating Livelihoods?            </p>
            <p
                class="mt-5 sm:mt-7 text-grey text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold text-justify"
            >
            At Al-Wahab Foundation, we strongly believe in creating stable incomes for impoverished families to secure brighter futures that positively impact entire communities.<br><br>Your generous donations enable us to offer tools and opportunities that establish new livelihoods for those living in disadvantaged areas. A fair and steady income not only empowers individuals but also supports entire households, promoting safety, better health, and protection from exploitation.<br><br>Our <span class="font-bold text-grey">Rozgar Project</span> focuses on providing vulnerable families with employment-related tools, such as rickshaws and delivery motorbikes, empowering them to work independently and generate a halal income. Your support makes a significant difference in transforming lives and uplifting communities.<br><br><span class="font-bold text-grey">The Messenger of Allah (swt) said, “It is better for any one of you to carry a bundle of wood on his back and sell it than to beg of someone whether he gives him or refuses.”- Al-Bukhari and Muslim</span><br><br>Your <a href="#" class="text-maroon hover:text-customBeige font-bold">donation of Zakat</a>  or <a href="#" class="text-maroon hover:text-customBeige font-bold">Sadaqah</a> has the power to change their lives with our innovative, long-term solutions to tackling poverty. When you give with AWF, you can be sure your donation will make a real difference to those in desperate need.

            </p>
            
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
