                class="mt-5 sm:mt-7 text-grey text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold text-justify"
            >
            Motorbikes have proven to be an excellent means of empowering people with employment opportunities. The <span class="text-grey font-bold">Rozgar Project</span> identifies individuals who are eager to work and possess the necessary skills but lack access to transportation to kick-start their careers. Through <a href="#" class="text-maroon hover:text-customBeige font-bold">generous donations</a> and community support, the project provides motorbikes to these individuals, enabling them to venture into delivery services for local businesses.
            </p>
            
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="row">
            <p
                class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl text-maroon font-bold mt-10 sm:mt-20"
            >
            Our Achievement So Far…!            </p>
            <p
                class="mt-5 sm:mt-7 text-grey text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold text-justify"
            >
            Under the vision of chairman Mufti Abdul Wahab and the generous support from our valued donors, Al-Wahab Foundation has successfully provided a total of 73 rickshaws and 130 motorbikes. This initiative has had a significant impact by creating sustainable income sources for 980 beneficiaries. Through these efforts, we are empowering individuals to achieve financial stability and a brighter future for themselves and their families. We remain dedicated to our mission of uplifting lives and making a positive difference in the communities we serve, all made possible by the collective support and dedication of our donors and team.
            </p>
            
        </div>
    </div>

    <!--section 4 -->
   
        <div class="flex justify-center mt-10 sm:mt-12">
